Knight Industries Assembly libraries
====================================


Calling AES functions
---------------------

All AES calls are made using their name (eg appl_init)
with the parameters passed after the name.

format:

	call_name()	intin values, addrin values


Resource Objects
----------------

To use scroll bars the following extended types are used

1 = Vertical slider
2 = Horizontal slider
3 = Up arrow
4 = Down arrow
5 = Left arrow
6 = Right arrow
7 = Vertical Scroll bar
8 = Horizontal Scroll bar

9  = Horizontal colour bar (uses vdi)
10 = Horizontal colour bar Left arrow
11 = Horizontal colour bar Right arrow


Resource Order
--------------

Scroll bars:   left/up arrow,  right/down arrow, slider parent, slider